://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Copa America\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"the selection\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never had the chance to be in the Olympic Games and I would love to,\\\" said Romero.\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1045, \"end\": 1051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\", \"score\": 0.7694523531450086, \"rank\": 0.1288217668555633, \"text\": \"Romero\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._C._Romero\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, it does not depend on me, but if you want to take me I am available for the Argentine national team.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1142, \"end\": 1165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999773379800816, \"rank\": 2.2661545422228956e-05, \"text\": \"Argentine national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I continue with the same enthusiasm and desire as always to continue doing things well at the club to continue having the possibility of being here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same enthusiasm\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"desire\", \"from